%% 3.2.3 Edit Account (Staff) — sequence (layered)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Super Admin
    participant UI as UI (/accounts)
    participant UC as Controller (UserController)
    participant US as Service (UserService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository User)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Note over Actor,DB: Route guard BR10

    UI->>UC: GET /api/User/Get/{id}
    UC-->>UI: pre-fill modal

    Actor->>UI: Save Update
    UI->>UC: PUT /api/User/Update/{id} UserUpdateDto
    UC->>US: UpdateUserAsync

    alt Email already exists
        US-->>UC: throw
        UC-->>UI: 400
        UI-->>Actor: Inline email error
    else OK
        US->>Repo: Update user
        Repo->>DB: UPDATE
        UC-->>UI: 200 — table refresh, role badge
    end
